Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:12.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness still continues to stalk me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:32.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle lit within
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is lively;\Nthe chandeliers are gorgeous, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:43.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I fill the hole left behind\Nby those lacking words?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:46.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least swim freely\Nin my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:56.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't need a sky like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can face tomorrow without painting\Nover all the things up to yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:22.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:39.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers who keep\Na close eye on the countless souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,good and evil, that fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:47.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,While visiting the Visoreds,\NIchigo, after intense Visored Training,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,finally succeeds in suppressing\Nhis inner Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:55.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, conducting his investigation\Nat the Daireisho Archives,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake finds a possible clue\Nto Aizen's goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:04.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to kill the Soul Society's\NRoyal Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:09.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen attempts to create the Ouken,\Nthe key to enter the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:14.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And to do so he needs\N100,000 souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and an Enriched Spirit Zone\Nin the radius of one spirit mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Karakura Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as all the nearby\Nland and people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:25.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will be ripped away from\Nthe world and will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:29.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait one moment, Captain Hitsugaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:37.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who's been\Nwaiting here to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsugaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:03.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You've awakened, Hinamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for you to be walking\Naround already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...I'm all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like\Nyou're all right, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:29.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry, Hitsugaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...for not believing in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:41.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something wrong with me\Nfor pointing my sword at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...\NThat won't bother me forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bother me,\Nso don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:52.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some sleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of those bags\Nunder your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Thank you, Hitsugaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get a lot more\Nsleep than other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll stop growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to catch up to her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you sleep for\Nat least ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:24.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up! Rangiku is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Hitsugaya, you of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't talk to me about growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "Hitsugaya,"\Nit's "Captain Hitsugaya."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:59.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...\NCan I ask you something, Hitsugaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:12.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to...\Nfight Captain Aizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:19.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Captain Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:30.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What Captain Aizen is doing is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:37.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure that he has\Na good reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Captain Aizen is\Nbeing forced by Captain Ichimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or someone else, into doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:55.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I let her talk out of respect\Nfor her wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it seems that it's still too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!\NYour power's dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:34.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Help Sado out\Nwith his training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:41.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like\Nhe'll leave if I turn him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not answering my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not such a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be big-hearted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, outsiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked you, didn't he?\NThen you should help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You need the power of a Bankai\Nto train Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, even more so,\Nyou should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a Bankai, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,OH COME ON!\N\N	    \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	Oh, come on! A mere handsome\N	and perverted shopkeeper like me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,OH COME ON!\N\N	    \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	would never be able to use a Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:23.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,OH COME ON!\N\N	 \N	    \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	Don't you know the details\N	of what's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:27.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,OH COME ON!\N\N	 \N	    \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	  \N	I've known for some time now that\N	you used to be the Squad 12 captain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:30.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you were the one\Nwho created the Hogyoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:36.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people say that\Nyoung people these days
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have no manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:45.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he asked you! You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to him, Ururu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the end,\Nhe doesn't have any manly spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:53.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He really doesn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As they say,\N"Those who don't work don't eat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I won't fall for that!\NYou're the same, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... I won't be any good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:20.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Bankai isn't good for training\Npeople or helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:28.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I understand! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:29.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, you have something\Nyou want to ask me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do routine chores\Naround here for three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:46.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer any of your questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:49.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Helping with training\Nisn't a routine chore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:55.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is! You're still putting in effort\Nand risking your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you give up asking me\Nwhat you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so resistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:32.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Abarai is really getting into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:43.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You can't get strong\Nif you just run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:24.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado, your power still has\Nroom for growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:30.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to move on\Nto the next step
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:33.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if you keep fighting against a Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:40.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one concern...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:49.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is different from that\Nof a Soul Reaper or a Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... It's as if your power is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to undo\Nyour Hollow transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, stupid?!\NIt was dangerous if I hadn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Going as far\Nas you can is your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fool around, then quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are getting along\Nunexpectedly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:46.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat is walking across\Nthat wide area
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as if there's a rim around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:57.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds and the other animals\Ndon't approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No... They can't approach it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...there's a barrier here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:19.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a powerful barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's kind of like\Nmy Shunshunrikka shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:39.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Ichigo! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I got it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:54.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you that\Nthe first move you make
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,after you take out your mask is slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get hit...it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:07.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The time he can maintain that\Nstate isn't getting any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he won't make\Nimmediate progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:13.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:19.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, say, why is Berry doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:23.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the training to remain in\Nhis Hollow form for long periods of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro was able to remain\Nin her Hollow form
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for 15 hours from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one who didn't train
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to maintain a Hollow transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:40.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:44.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! Stupid Kensei, you grouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:44.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:50.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:56.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has passed through\Nmy barrier and entered this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:03.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hachigyo Sogai placed\Naround here is a technique
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:07.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I created when I became\Na Visored...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to disperse it\Nwith Soul Reaper kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a Visored like us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:19.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's most confusing is that\Nthe intruder didn't destroy my barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but passed through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:26.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think even a Visored\Ncould do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who in the world\Nis this intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:36.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- A...\N- A human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:58.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...\NWhere's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a joke.\NDon't get mad, Kensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say I was kidding\Nin this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:14.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...\NSo that's what's happening now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:33.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing... I was just thinking\Nthat you aren't very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:35.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I'm suddenly told
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,about something like\Nthis Ouken, the royal key,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my mind can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so worried, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:52.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. I'll stop Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still get stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for informing me, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NLet's begin training again, Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:09.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Ms. Hiyori", baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- I know...\N- I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki wasn't surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,not because his mind\Ncouldn't keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what\Nhis enemies' goals are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki only focuses\Non his own strength
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The surprise doesn't shake his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is really getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he isn't dark and scary like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just in a gentle way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:49.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Who was that woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:53.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She just talked to Ichigo and then left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like she was Ichigo's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...is Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:03.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What's this, Shinji?!\NYou know her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a blatant lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji, you always say\Nthat to cute girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You even said that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she implying that she's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He says that to all cute girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:22.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd! He's never said that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I didn't say it to you, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your barrier is perfect.\NThere's no mistaking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:39.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So how could that girl,\NOrihime, find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And furthermore, how could she get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:50.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But my impression of\Nher Spiritual Pressure up close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:54.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She has the same type of\Nbarrier-making abilities that I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I sensed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:18:00.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because of that ability
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that she was able to detect\Nthis place while it was in a barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as pass through my barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:11.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected a human\Nto have that kind of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:14.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So here you are, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:28.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke asked me to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:35.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted me to take you to\Nhis training ground immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tilt the goblet to the west, Wolke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hiding Gintô...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're calling me\Na coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!\NYou call that running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dodging speed is getting slower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your limit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My limit... He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:46.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My arms and legs can't move\Nmuch anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:51.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But his Spiritual Pressure\Nis definitely getting weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that my power\Nwould come back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if I kept dodging arrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is still no sign of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much of what\Nhe told me was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll kill me at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to stop his movements\Nand end this training!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And my only chance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My final Gintô!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:31.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The silver whip strikes\Nthe five-fingered stone bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:32.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:35.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:46.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:57.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:05.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To wear down both mind\Nand body to its limits
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:11.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and take a shot from a\Nspirit bow 19 mm to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of your heart's sinoatrial node...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:21.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to regain the powers\Nyou lost from Quincy Letz Stile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Why did you use a Gritz there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:34.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you used a Haizen,\Nyou could have at least injured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:40.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I say you're stupid.\NIt makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:46.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...I'll let that slide for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:54.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I dressed up my five fingers\Nwith a manicure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:22:00.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what's glowing\Nwas me instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration is like a goldfish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:06.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:09.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sound that\Ndoesn't bounce back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:25.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those lines stretching parallel\Nto each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:31.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They say one line turns beautiful,\Nthen deteriorate repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:36.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing right there, \Nbut the way is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:40.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance grows, \Nbut it's within reach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And even today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:51.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I trace your gibberish roman letters\Nover and over with my left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:23:01.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you see the moment\Nyou open your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:11.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What color will\Nhe paint your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:23.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, are you going to\Ncontinue training?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:25.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll get stronger if I stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:28.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll train him on\Nhis sense of humor too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When he leaves,\Nhe'll be a splendid Kansai Comedian!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:33.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... He's being taught genuine comedy!\NI'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:34.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:37.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:42.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, clean this room too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:44.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After we let Sado rest for\Nhalf an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to start his training again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:50.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:54.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting him to do general chores\Nin addition to training Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:57.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara really is good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:58.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He tricked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:01.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Pineapple, really is stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:02.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid...